      "difference_truncated": null,
      "encoding": null,
      "message": "perf Documentation: sysfs events/ interfaces\n\nAdd documentation for the <event>, <event>.scale, and <event>.unit\nfiles in sysfs.\n\n\t<event>.scale and <event>.unit were undocumented.\n\t<event> was previously documented only for specific powerpc pmu events.\n\nSigned-off-by: Cody P Schafer <34c6fceca75e456f25e7e99531e2425c6c1de443@codyps.com>\nSigned-off-by: Sukadev Bhattiprolu <2ac48ee9b8f6042694a5d86ef56b8e10fe5327d1@linux.vnet.ibm.com>\nCc: Andi Kleen <0474aee45985f5ae829f53849df476200e876990@linux.intel.com>\nCc: Anshuman Khandual <5cc840ad174e421baefc61e26aff2d5fb1883945@linux.vnet.ibm.com>\nCc: Cody P Schafer <34c6fceca75e456f25e7e99531e2425c6c1de443@codyps.com>\nCc: Haren Myneni <a828d6b576316e226a97a8449fa1587a63526294@us.ibm.com>\nCc: Haren Myneni <a828d6b576316e226a97a8449fa1587a63526294@us.ibm.com>\nCc: Jiri Olsa <2c6594f608aa3d41e98d48846a6328831f7084ad@redhat.com>\nCc: Michael Ellerman <ef2235e1fe17796ebeb6e6e3f3a0cc6684e255f6@au1.ibm.com>\nCc: Paul Mackerras <19a0ba370c443ba08d20b5061586430ab449ee8c@samba.org>\nCc: Peter Zijlstra <3fddac958924aef220f202ca567388ddab3f14a8@infradead.org>\nCc: Stephane Eranian <f199ae9781930a5b94b284ca2f471140752002a7@google.com>\nCc: 624e0123bdcc7ea450e9efbcd399e8858e365d3e@lists.ozlabs.org\nLink: http://lkml.kernel.org/r/1412143402-26061-4-git-send-email-2ac48ee9b8f6042694a5d86ef56b8e10fe5327d1@linux.vnet.ibm.com\nSigned-off-by: Arnaldo Carvalho de Melo <293abb6b76d7791c0732cc517d38c4b5c734b87f@redhat.com>\n",
